06:50.900 --> 06:59.560
No matter whether it's a short story or a novel, and no matter how complex the ultimate product might be,

06:59.720 --> 07:05.040
originally there always is the single image somewhere along the line that everything else generated from.

07:05.040 --> 07:10.560
