13:35.960 --> 13:41.720
And her Cinnabar was not quite the same as mine, but still there was something of the feeling about it,

13:41.720 --> 13:50.240
the almost surrealistic image of the city wavering on the horizon of the city which is totally cut off from the entire rest of the world.

13:50.240 --> 13:53.920
