14:16.100 --> 14:26.000
including the possibility of doing five novelettes which would come together as another make-up novel about the character Jade Blue.

14:26.420 --> 14:34.500
My publisher and I would like to do a new edition of Cinnabar with a brand new Cinnabar story in it.

14:35.080 --> 14:39.520
