But it also shows that good research can cover a multitude of sins.

26:57.660 --> 27:03.140
He maintains that even with the hard science elements, particle theory is still a people story.

27:03.580 --> 27:06.680
This story for me is still a people story, first and foremost.

27:06.680 --> 27:09.940
It's, again, about relationships of people.

27:10.480 --> 27:17.660
And the scientific content amplifies, illustrates, and I hope clarifies those relationships.

27:18.020 --> 27:23.160
But, by God, the people still come first and the science and technology come second.

27:29.340 --> 27:33.740
Bryant's first published short story collection, Among the Dead, came out in 1973.

27:34.200 --> 27:37.140
It contains a number of stories written early in his career.

27:37.400 --> 27:43.300
His novel, Phoenix Without Ashes, is in fact a novelization of Harlan Ellison's original pilot script

27:43.300 --> 27:46.540
for the ill-fated television series, The Star Lost.

27:46.760 --> 27:48.100
This work is a rarity.

27:48.100 --> 27:53.020
As a novelization, which came after the fact, it is actually a solid piece of work.

27:53.200 --> 27:55.780
The planned sequels have never materialized.

27:56.120 --> 27:59.440
Certainly, Edward Bryant has established himself as a top-flight writer,

27:59.580 --> 28:02.640
who happens also to work under the label science fiction.

